@startuml
title Autonomous Org Full-Loop Plan

skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Noto Sans CJK KR

package "Current Completed Core" {
  [TL Routing]
  [Engineer Implementation]
  [Review / QA Participation]
  [Close / Merge Candidate]
  [Real-Org E2E]
  [Knowledge Setup UI]
}

package "P0 Highest Priority" {
  [Organizational Memory Ingest]
  [Human -> PM Intake]
  [QA Gate Policy]
}

package "P1 Retrieval / Operator" {
  [Operator Pin / Hide UI]
  [Candidate / Final-Hit Cache]
  [Chunk-Link Multi-Hop]
}

package "P2 Long-Term Learning" {
  [Quality Trend Surface]
  [Cross-Issue Memory]
  [External Agent Feedback]
}

[TL Routing] --> [Engineer Implementation]
[Engineer Implementation] --> [Review / QA Participation]
[Review / QA Participation] --> [Close / Merge Candidate]
[Close / Merge Candidate] --> [Organizational Memory Ingest]
[Real-Org E2E] --> [Organizational Memory Ingest]
[Knowledge Setup UI] --> [Organizational Memory Ingest]

[Human -> PM Intake] --> [TL Routing]
[QA Gate Policy] --> [Review / QA Participation]
[Organizational Memory Ingest] --> [Operator Pin / Hide UI]
[Organizational Memory Ingest] --> [Candidate / Final-Hit Cache]
[Organizational Memory Ingest] --> [Chunk-Link Multi-Hop]
[Operator Pin / Hide UI] --> [Quality Trend Surface]
[Candidate / Final-Hit Cache] --> [Quality Trend Surface]
[Chunk-Link Multi-Hop] --> [Cross-Issue Memory]
[External Agent Feedback] --> [Cross-Issue Memory]

note bottom
Priority:
P0 (memory + intake + QA policy)
-> P1 (operator/retrieval quality)
-> P2 (learning surfaces)
end note

@enduml
